      "description": "No Chris - Tumbling Daisies Trio\n\nSHOW\nLoad In: 5:30-6:00 pm\nSoundcheck: 6 pm\nSet Time: 7-8:50 pm\nSHOW DETAILS\n● Set Length: Two 45-minute sets with a short break in between.\n● Set Flow: Please begin your performance with a quieter song or two, then build from\nthere. We’re a restaurant first, and want guests to feel welcome to stay and dine before\nthe room ramps up.\n● Stage Curfew: End time 8:50 pm, strick 9 pm curfew\n● Stage Size: 16” X 12”\nLOAD-IN / SOUND\n\n● Load-In Location: Please load-in though our front door. You may pull up and put your\nhazard lights on to unload.\n● Timing: A sound technician will be onsite one hour before your set for soundcheck.\nArtists should plan to load in 30 minutes prior to that and be ready to set up the stage at\nthat one-hour mark. If you need additional load-in time, please coordinate with the Talent\nBooker in advance so staff can be prepared to assist and provide direction.\n● Parking: We do not have reserved artist parking. Our lot fills quickly. We recommend\nstreet parking on 2nd Street or nearby areas without “No Parking” signage.\n● Soundcheck: Takes place one hour before set time.\nBACKLINE:\n● Drum Kit, Keyboard, Amps backline available, see Backline/Tech Ryder.\nGREEN ROOM / HOSPITALITY\n● Hospitality: A family-style meal will be placed in the green room before your set.\nHospitality is based on the number of performers in your act.\n● Green Room Timing: Please clear the green room within 30 minutes after your set\nends.\n\nPAYMENT\nAnimales uses a hybrid guarantee model:\n● You’ll receive a guaranteed base pay, which is made up of audience tips (confirmed with\nyou directly in advance).\n● Audience tips (via Venmo QR, table QR codes, and physical tip jars) go directly to you.\n● If tips fall short of your guarantee, Animales covers the difference.\n● If tips exceed the guarantee, you keep the full amount.\n● Tip payouts: Cash tips are paid out in cash the same night. Any cash tips will be\ndeducted from the check amount, and the balance paid by check. Digital tips are paid by\ncheck.\n\n--\nShowtime: 7pm-9pm\nCover: Free",
